<% content_for :title, "Brand Guidelines" %>

<div class="overview">
  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    Hey folks! üëã From logos to phrasing, we want to make sure you and your team feel confident sharing about Hack Club / HCB on your site, fundraising platforms, grant apps, and other online spaces.
  </p>
  <p>
    We know you‚Äôre eager to share about your nonprofit status through HCB. ü§ó Following brand guidelines will not only help you display an accurate relationship with Hack Club but will also help create a unified appearance amongst all fiscally sponsored projects and legitimize your status.
  </p>
  <% fs_callout_title = capture do %>
    Jump to <%= link_to "the fiscal sponsorship section", "#fiscal-sponsorship", style: "color: inherit;" %>
    to see how you can accurately represent your 501(c)(3) status.
  <% end %>
  <%= render "callout", type: "info", title: fs_callout_title %>
